CustomField.description: This is the Apex class that will be injected into the process execution. If the domain process type is "Criteria", then the class has to implement IDomainProcessCriteria or IDomainProcessCriteriaWithExistingRecs. If the domain process type is "Action", then the class has to implement IDomainProcessAction or IDomainProcessActionWithExistingRecs
CustomField.inlineHelpText: This is the Apex class that will be injected into the process execution.
CustomField.label: Class To Inject
